snippet.textDisplay: With Tamil, you will be learning one of the oldest languages of the human kind. To enjoy the songs, you had better learn both the Centamil (the formal form) and the contemporary form. The first is the expanded proper version (used in reading news, singing songs and court communications). The contemporary one, being used as per the region one is in.
